<emphasis italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">peepthong</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="32" pageNumber="33" type="range">
<paragraph pageId="32" pageNumber="33">Range.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="32" pageNumber="33">China, Taiwan, Laos, Myanmar, Thailand, and Vietnam. Widely distributed in Myanmar.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="32" pageNumber="33" type="use">
<paragraph pageId="32" pageNumber="33">Use.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="32" pageNumber="33">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">Bark</emphasis>
: Used as antidote in alcohol poisoning.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
